  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nadd support for sending requests via ipc for\r\n- [ ] unix\r\n- [ ] windows (named pipes)\r\n\r\n\r\nadding this on UNIX should be fairly simple by creating a new file at the configured location and connecting via `tokio::UnixStream`\r\n\r\nref https://github.com/servo/ipc-channel\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
